APSYS, Securing complex projects

APSYS is specialised in value creation through technical, human and
operational risks control. It offers innovative consulting and software
solutions with a high level scientific and technological integration.
Designing even more reliable aircraft, securing autonomous vehicles,
anticipating the nuclear installation obsolescence or protecting industrial
assets against cyber-attacks are the challenges for which APSYS employees
expertise contributes on a daily basis.

   EN SAVOIR PLUS

PRODUCT SECURITY

Our APSYS Product Security business unit addresses products and
their industrial environments throughout their lifecycle, including physical
products, data / information and processes. This implies a definition of the
Risk Analysis strategy and the establishment of appropriate and
effective means of protection.

   EN SAVOIR PLUS

PRODUCT ASSURANCE & SAFETY
AEROSPACE

Our Aerospace Business Unit offers solutions combining
state-of-the-art and innovation (analyses and software) for the
management of risks in the aerospace industry. Our team of specialists
and experts operates with consulting firms, maintenance
organisations, airlines and airports.

   EN SAVOIR PLUS

PRODUCT ASSURANCE & SAFETY
TRANSPORT, ENERGY, DEFENCE

Our proposals are based on APSYS’ historical business in terms
of risk management, in particular in the field of Operational Safety and
Integrated Logistic Support, to support the design of systems in the
sectors of Automotive, Rail and Defence.

   EN SAVOIR PLUS

DIGITAL & SOFTWARE

Digital solutions to optimise cost during product lifecycle.
APSYS is an active participant in companies digitalisation through
the distribution of Model-Based engineering tools (SIMFIA, SIMLOG)
and Maintenance Information Systems solutions (AMASIS).

   EN SAVOIR PLUS

