TESTIMONIES

     * " Risk coverage is ensured by both functional and technical
       requirements, and also by the setting up of diagnostics. These
       diagnostics will be directly implanted within the vehicle. They
       will either allow the customer to be made aware of a risk by a
       warning light, or switch the system to a safe state, with the main
       objective of continuing to ensure the protection of the customer. "
       MAROUANE,
       DEPENDABILITY ENGINEER
