       information from one country to another. Secondly, I support Michel
       Oberlé (Head of Export) in his mission to seize new opportunities
       around the world. To do this, I conduct markets studies and
       implement a technological watch strategy in innovative sectors,
       such as drones and autonomous vehicles. In parallel to my studies
       I’m happy to participate in the consolidation of the APSYS global
       commercial strategy. Apsys applies principles of integrity and a
       code of business conduct (Ethics & Compliance program). This is a
       new field for me, but thanks to my close collaboration with Michel,
       we are leading the project together to develop and disseminate
       secure practices, compliance and ethical processes and attitudes
       within the company and its subsidiaries. I’m very proud to
       contribute to the evolution of the company and thankful for having
       this opportunity within the APSYS team! 3 values: Expertise,
       Innovation et Team spirit. "
       ESTHER,
       EXPORT AND SUBSIDIARIES SALES AND COMMUNICATION ASSISTANT
     * " I’m currently doing a master’s degree in international human
